<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Australian amateur cooks are stocking up on a new southern fried chicken offering at Coles supermarkets, calling it the perfect addition to any burger.</p>

<p>One woman shared a photo of her KFC-inspired dinner on social media, complete with a hearty burger and a side of chips, crediting the grocer for its new range.</p>

<p>'How to make a fried chicken burger. I used the Aldi brioche buns, hands down my favourite... I always go out of my way to buy them,' she said.</p>

<p>'Then I bought Coles southern fried chicken in the meat section and Coles special burger sauce, which we are obsessed with and use as a chip dip as well.'</p>

<p>One woman shared a photo of her KFC-inspired dinner on social media, complete with a hearty burger and a side of chips, crediting the grocer for its new range</p>

<p>Finally a handful of potatoes were cooked in an air fryer for maximum crispiness and enjoyed alongside the burger.</p>

<p>The chicken, which is $8.50, can be bought as a breast piece or thighs, as well as tenders, depending on what kind of meal you want to put together.</p>

<p>The chicken, which is $8.50, can be bought as a breast piece or thighs (pictured)</p>

<p>They are to be cooked at 180C Celsius for 30-35 minutes and turned once at the 15-minute mark.</p>

<p>Plenty of people on Facebook said they also enjoyed making burgers with them, suggesting they were the perfect amount of 'crispiness'.</p>

<p>'Yummmmm. That Coles southern fried chicken is really tasty,' said one person.</p>

<p>'We do our Coles KFC-style chicken in the air fryer. It's definitely not spicy, otherwise I would not eat it,' said another.</p>

<p>A third added: 'Well that's dinner on the weekend sorted then'. </p>

<p>Purchase Aldi's brioche buns, Coles' southern fried chicken, lettuce, tomato and Coles' special burger sauce and a layer of cheese.</p>

<p>Oven bake the southern fried chicken at 180C for 30-35 minutes, flipping it over at the 15-minute mark. </p>

<p>Once each ingredient is stacked on the other, air fry a handful of potatoes to dip into the special burger sauce. </p>

<p>Southern fried chicken is a dish that consists of chicken pieces that have been coated in a seasoned batter and pan-fried, deep-fried or pressure fried</p>

<p>Southern fried chicken is a dish that consists of chicken pieces that have been coated in a seasoned batter and are pan-fried, deep-fried or pressure fried.   </p>

<p>The breading adds a crisp coating or crust to the chicken while retaining the juices in the meat.</p>

<p>It was actually a dish created by the Scottish, who brought it to America, according to The Daily Meal.   </p>
